OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTeacher sacked for sending 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmaskless vulnerable boy out
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fof class                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A teacher who sent a vulnerable pupil  
OL,6, from class for taking off his facemask 
OL,7, to sip water has been sacked.          
OL,9,FThe 15-year-old was told to leave just 
OL,10,F38 seconds after arriving in the lesson
OL,11,Fat St Clare's School, in Porthcawl,    
OL,12,FBridgend county, a tribunal heard.     
OL,14,FThe tribunal report said the teenager  
OL,15,Fhad "documented additional learning and
OL,16,Fbehavioural needs".                    
OL,18,FIt added that after the teacher ordered
OL,19,Fthe boy out in December 2020 she forgot
OL,20,Fshe had done so.                       
